	            		                  <div class="capa4">
	            		                      <div class="punto"></div>
	            		                      <h4>Esporles to Banyalbufar Highway (Ma-1100)</h4>
	            		                      <p class="datos">Distance 0.933 km - Time 15 minutes  - Altitude 225 m -  N39 40'7.918" E2 34'4.962"</p>
	            		                      <p class="desc">Cross the highway and continue parallel to it for 10 min., then, when you cross it again, this time to the left, the irregularly paved stone path gently rises and crosses two portholes.</p>
	            		                  </div>
